<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ yào bǎ nǐ dài xiàng gāo chù 迦南1398</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yào bǎ nǐ dài xiàng gāo chù, zài dà hǎi zhōng wèi nǐ kāi lù,
 zhǔ kàn nǐ rú yǎn zhōng de tóng rén, zhǔ kàn nǐ rú zhǎng shàng de míng zhū,
 zhǔ yào ràng nǐ wěn xíng zài gāo chù, zài kuàng yě zhōng wèi nǐ kāi lù,
 nǐ yào chéng wèi zhòng rén de zhù fú, bǎ xǔ duō xǔ duō de rén lái jiān gù,
 yǎng wàng yé sū tā shì wǒ de fēng fù, shì wǒ de róng yào shì wǒ de mǎn zú,
 gāng qiáng zhàn wěn bù yào hòu gù, zhǔ yīng xǔ wǒ fēng yǔ gòng dù.
 zhǔ yīng xǔ wǒ fēng yǔ gòng dù.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1398</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>